<title>USA: ASM/Applied Materials in mediation.</title>
<headline>ASM/Applied Materials in mediation.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>ASM International NV said Monday that, at the request of the U.S. District Court in San Jose, it and Applied Materials are involved in mediation.</p>
<p>To permit the mediation to proceed, all litigation between the parties has been temporarily stayed, a news release issued by ASM said.</p>
<p>ASM International is headquartered in Bilthoven, The Netherlands. ASM International's subsidiaries design, manufacture and market equipment and materials used to produce semiconductor devices.</p>
